    description: 'Thermal differentials reveal trapped moisture beneath roofing membranes that visual inspection cannot detect. AI classifies severity and maps affected square footage for targeted remediation.',
    detection: 'Post-sunset thermal surveys exploit differential cooling rates between wet and dry insulation.',
    cost: 'Targeted repair before water reaches critical infrastructure below.',
  },
  {
    id: 'hot-spots',
    icon: 'electric_bolt',
