    summary: 'Overloaded connections and failing components identified aerially.',
    description: 'External switchgear, transformers, and bus connections emit thermal signatures when connections degrade. Aerial surveys cover entire electrical infrastructure in minutes, satisfying NFPA 70B requirements.',
